{"id": 2403, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得现如今你的叛逆精神都体现在哪了？", "description": "你们都喜欢流川枫但我喜欢仙道，你们都喜欢白雪公主但我喜欢后妈。（题图来自：视觉中国 © Ikon Images）", "record_count": 8686, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180607184426S1UetZNvKIi2nhao.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-06-19T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 288000, "content": "男女绝对平等", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377883}, {"id": 288001, "content": "坚决不相亲", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 506208}, {"id": 288002, "content": "喜欢大张伟", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1344396}, {"id": 288258, "content": "世界杯白痴", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1303661}, {"id": 288003, "content": "到现在不看101", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 152656}, {"id": 288771, "content": "要有誓死不屈服的决心", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380667}, {"id": 288004, "content": "从来都觉得规矩就是用来打破的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1123251}, {"id": 288772, "content": "要有誓死不屈服的决心", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380667}, {"id": 288005, "content": "就是宅着，然后现在，额-_-", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1289651}, {"id": 289542, "content": "无聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1371453}, {"id": 288007, "content": "边吐槽网剧不按小说拍，边看的津津有味！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377927}, {"id": 288263, "content": "我认定的事，谁说都没用", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378592}, {"id": 288264, "content": "烂梗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 894776}, {"id": 288009, "content": "不刻意与众不同，不跟风追潮流，做想做的事，读书学习健身早睡早起", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1375460}, {"id": 288265, "content": "坚决不去动物园和海洋馆，那是动物监狱", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1337395}, {"id": 288010, "content": "抗拒自拍", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 736221}, {"id": 289290, "content": "视金钱如粪土上的苍蝇，追着拍。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1379658}, {"id": 288011, "content": "不玩游戏，任何游戏", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377936}, {"id": 289803, "content": "在围墙里讨论人身的自由", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1386256}, {"id": 288268, "content": "年轻人流行玩什么看什么，我就会去尝试！不想在我身上延续年代的鄙视链。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378600}, {"id": 289036, "content": "不想学习，不想考研", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1363393}, {"id": 289805, "content": "在警营里怀念大学的美好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1386256}, {"id": 288014, "content": "爸妈叫我学习我不学", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1062896}, {"id": 289038, "content": "喝中药偏要加白砂糖  我们不一样?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1382963}, {"id": 288015, "content": "相信梦想", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1367491}, {"id": 288016, "content": "成为有趣的人", "image": "img/option/option/20180619164731qruUhHkTDGOPRdMo", "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 327081}, {"id": 288017, "content": "不叛逆", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 682910}, {"id": 288018, "content": "我好像还没叛逆?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1371145}, {"id": 290322, "content": "从不随大流，最讨厌别人说那么多人都看/玩/做，你不弄就是错误", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1335444}, {"id": 288019, "content": "不得不思虑更多可心里还是拒接长大", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1306722}, {"id": 290323, "content": "人家赖床睡懒觉，我晨练吃早餐\n人家上课玩手机，我看杂书小说\n人家乘车玩手机，我APP看书摘\n人家打游戏吹空调，我健身房撸铁／练舞\n人家半夜蹦野迪，我听书练瑜伽\n人家外卖／餐厅，我样样自己来\n人家三餐看心情，我也随心情（啊哈哈总算有个随大流）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1389278}, {"id": 288020, "content": "我不叛逆，只是按照自己心意做事而已", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1351084}, {"id": 290324, "content": "大家口渴了：冰阔落！冰维他！冰棍儿！\n我：（日常随身茶杯）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1389278}, {"id": 288021, "content": "你们都有女朋友，而我没有?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1304517}, {"id": 289045, "content": "死宅！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1355673}, {"id": 288022, "content": "不刷朋友圈，不发朋友圈\n不下载微博抖音快手\n不看国内综艺选秀等等节目\n不关心当红明星电视剧等等", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1370937}, {"id": 288534, "content": "坚持认为自己是个特别的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 32845}, {"id": 292119, "content": "你们在学习的时候，我在玩。你们在玩的时候，我在睡觉。你们在睡觉的时候，我在这个地方写评论。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1396735}, {"id": 288024, "content": "gyakusou", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1316237}, {"id": 288792, "content": "别人都在夜修上认真学习而我在看好奇心日报", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1379744}, {"id": 288025, "content": "不看电视", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 563935}, {"id": 288537, "content": "做自己喜欢的 不在乎别人的看法 自己高兴就好 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1364689}, {"id": 288026, "content": "不打农药，不吃鸡?", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1358754}, {"id": 288027, "content": "从不强迫自己对自己不喜欢的人笑脸相迎。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1372742}, {"id": 288284, "content": "坚决不追星", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1082777}, {"id": 288029, "content": "大家都在吹牛逼 我偏偏要吹得更大", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1190636}, {"id": 288797, "content": "从不玩绝地求生，不玩抖音，手机只有微博微信和QQ，老年人了估计", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380759}, {"id": 288030, "content": "年轻时酷爱外国电影长大了又开始追8090年代的动漫", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377952}, {"id": 288031, "content": "不追求当下流行色", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1357767}, {"id": 288543, "content": "不看抖音不看综艺，不用网易云，一个人看电影吃晚饭，周边都在找女朋友依旧一个人不将就", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1258692}]}